  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, cumin, paprika, and salt.",
    "Rub the mixture all over the chicken breasts.",
    "Grill the chicken for 5-6 minutes per side, or until charred and cooked through.",
    "Let the chicken rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "Warm the tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing sliced chicken onto a tortilla, followed by radishes, avocado, and cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
